规定，但在入职半个月后却突然被要求参与一场没有标准答案、与自己岗位职责关联也不大的考试。 在考试后他就遭到无补偿解雇，“没有什么理由，最后也只是给了我这工作半个月的底薪。” 编辑：周芝逸 责编：李奇 审核：阮鹏程 完整内容来源全天禁止员工用手机、出大门，违反就要打扫卫生？小鹿妈妈被立案调查_公司_规定_限制"},"attached_info":"CkIIjqevjdH/8vIbEAMaCTExNDE4MTgxNCD0wo6/BjAAON4LQBZyCzE1NzUwMjQ1ODY2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"58 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d0c146e13fb6e983dcf11461a9248e88_1440w.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"23_1743082203.531538","card_id":"Q_15663399987","target":{"id":15663399987,"title":"农村为什么要通自来水？之前井水挺甜清凉，现在的自来水总感觉有味道，通自来水是为了收费吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/15663399987","type":"question","created":1742798172,"answer_count":813,"follower_count":1190,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[5380],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"农村之前都是自己家里可以直接用井水，为什么现在要村村通自来水，还要收费"},"attached_info":"CkIIjqevjdH/8vIbEAMaCTExNDE0NTY1NyDc+oO/BjAAOKYJQBdyCzE1NjYzMzk5OTg3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"57 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-da57141d22544414e8e0c2c8b4580b68_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"24_1743082203.531901","card_id":"Q_15329933697","target":{"id":15329933697,"title":"怎样才能爱上学英语?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/15329933697","type":"question","created":1742364811,"answer_count":29,"follower_count":106,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2748],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"在英语学习中获得不了成就感，或者说学习同样学过的知识再次学习就没有什么动力"},"attached_info":"CkEIjqevjdH/8vIbEAMaCTExNDA1ODg0MSCLwem+BjAAOGpAGHILMTUzMjk5MzM2OTd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"56 万热度","trend":0,"